SUMMARY:July 2026 General Meeting
DTSTAMP:20260626T100758Z
DTSTART:20260713T183000Z
DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendars! The Houston Heights Association’s Great Am
	erican Pie Contest is coming to our General Meeting on Monday\, July 13 at
	 6:30 PM. \nThink your pie recipe is the best in the Heights? Enter one of
	 our four categories: \n\n\nSweet \n\n\nSavory \n\n\nJunior Baker \n\n\nPr
	esentation \n\n\nContestants are required to enter 2 pies for judging\, an
	d a panel of 6 judges will decide who takes home bragging rights as the He
	ights’ top pie baker of 2026. Prizes will be awarded for 1st\, 2nd\, and 3
	rd place in each category. There will also be a Best Presentation Award\, 
	selected by People’s Choice\, so be sure to bring your creativity along wi
	th your baking skills! \nWhether you’re baking or just cheering on your ne
	ighbors\, everyone is invited to join the fun. Bring your appetite and you
	r community spirit—we can’t wait to see you there! \n\nSUBMIT YOUR PIE\n\n
	https://houstonheights.org/event/july-2026-general-meeting/\n\nFrom Housto
	n Heights Association
URL:https://houstonheights.org/event/july-2026-general-meeting/
LOCATION:Houston Heights City Hall & Fire Station\, 107 W. 12th Street\, Ho
	uston\, TX\, 77008\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:houston-heights-association
CATEGORIES:Houston Heights Association
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
