		\n				TICKETING INFO\nSeason tickets are now available. 6-show packages s
	tart at just $34 per-show. \nTickets will start at $46 and will be availab
	le beginning July 13 online or by calling TUTS Guest Services at 713-558-8
	887. Tickets will also available in person Monday through Friday from Noon
	 to 6 p.m. at the TUTS Box Office\, located in the Hobby Center lobby. \nD
	iscounted group tickets are available for parties of 10 or more.Theatre Un
	der The Stars has a variety of accessibility options for guests.Learn more
	 about accessible performances and other services here. \nRush tickets wil
	l be available for $35 at the box office for mezzanine and gallery seating
	 starting 2 hours prior to curtain. \nQuestions about parking\, dining or 
